[Shandong province is the next province north of Jiangsu. Jiangxi province shares borders with both Anhui and Zhejiang provinces. It is not clear whether the farmer became infected in Jiangxi or Zhejiang, but perhaps H7N9 originated in Jiangxi, or even further south, and is moving north with summer migrating wildfowl. - Mod.JW]

Maps of China can be seen at http://www.sacu.org/maps/provmap.png and http://healthmap.org/r/1zaU. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]

